OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWe're fully booked up, says
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Florry driving trainer      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has announced it is     
OL,6, boosting the number of places available
OL,7, on its skills scheme to try to address 
OL,8, a chronic shortage of lorry drivers.   
OL,10,FIt has increased funding for its HGV   
OL,11,FSkills Bootcamps from #17m to #34m,    
OL,12,Fallowing them to offer 11,000 places   
OL,13,Finstead of 5,000.                      
OL,15,FBut one training firm, 2 Start, told   
OL,16,Fthe BBC the system could not cope.     
OL,18,F"We are fully booked up until April and
OL,19,Fwe are not alone," said managing       
OL,20,Fdirector Paul Moon.                    
